Awp_baem by BaShoR

This map was originally a project from me for a famous German Clan.
But because of some Problems with the Management I finished it in a private project
and now im releasing it, to share it with the world.

Features:
*Dust Soundscape and some Special Sounds
*3D Skybox
*Full "High Dynamic Range" Lighting
*Overview and Navigation
*Customtextures and Eastereggs
*On Lan tested Gameplay
*18 Playerslots
*Complete Optimized Map even on "Low PCs" +50 FPS
*Grafically interesting Brushwork

Special thanks to
my 2D Designer reave
my Supporter toOuri
my Bugfinder Frontschwein

and the other guys mentioned in the credit texture.


For Bugfixes please contact me under sfs-cooldragon@web.de
